name: sky_protect_dim_2
description: Populates Sky Protect dimension tables that are not dependencies for a fact table

source_to_target.name: current_flag
source_to_target.transformation: case when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.current_flag = '1' then true when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.current_flag = '0' then false end

source_to_target.name: allow_email
source_to_target.transformation: case when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.allow_email = 1 then true when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.allow_email = 0 end

source_to_target.name: allow_sms
source_to_target.transformation: case when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.allow_sms = 1 then true when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.allow_sms = 0 end

source_to_target.name: allow_campaign_email
source_to_target.transformation: case when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.allow_campaign_email = 1 then true when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.allow_campaign_email = 0 then true end

source_to_target.name: deceased
source_to_target.transformation: case when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.deceased = 1 then true when uk_tds_ice_eod_is.cc_ice_dim_party.deceased = 0 then true end

author: Sean Conkie
